  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>UBERSLAUGHTER </i></strong>  <br><br>Endure relentless waves of enemies in a retro, trippy, dopaminergic onslaught.<br><br>You play as Reapin Randy, a dimension-hopping drugged-up bloodthirsty maniac with questionable ethics. <br><br>Brace yourself for an intense FPS journey filled with gore, action, and the occasional cute animal.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/0379d7a1972e97bb69a5c51d14b1f90d.poster.avif?t=1773002792\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/0379d7a1972e97bb69a5c51d14b1f90d.webm?t=1773002792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/0379d7a1972e97bb69a5c51d14b1f90d.mp4?t=1773002792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/e79ff294ee7096ec39a4b9e81bd07681.avif?t=1773002792\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/2a99cbfc0e95f403102cd7e77bc6eaee.poster.avif?t=1773002792\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/2a99cbfc0e95f403102cd7e77bc6eaee.webm?t=1773002792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595540/extras/2a99cbfc0e95f403102cd7e77bc6eaee.mp4?t=1773002792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_i